metadata.description: There has long been an uneasy peace between the various Queens of the realm of Wonderland.  But with the arrival of the goddess of death, Keres, it is a peace that will not last. Vying for control of the realm of madness each Queen has brought an army to the battle that will determine the true ruler of Wonderland! The newest Wonderland series from the company that defines fantasy and horror has arrived.
metadata.name: Wonderland: Clash of Queens
